Authorization Kata
------------------

In the travel business an employee can travel just if three kind
of authorizers allows the travel.

In order to travel you need:
a set of OKs by the your authorizers and 1 OK by your Risk
authorizer

The risk authorizer should vote always yes and he says no only if the
trip has a connection with one of those places because very dangerous:

 * NAP
 * ROM
 * GOA


The override authorizer can force the travel at anytime because he has the
role to skip all other checks

Each authorized can vote just once

Elephant Carpaccio
------------------

 Always on trip
 Add travel with departure and arrival places
 Only one authorizer
 Just different authorizers
 Add the risk authorizers with always yes
 The risk understand places
 Add the override authorizer

